      <div dir="ltr">If you are using instance types that support SR-IOV
        (aka. "enhanced networking" in AWS), then turn it on. We saw
        huge differences when SR-IOV is enabled
        <div>
          <div class="gmail_extra"><br>
          </div>
          <div class="gmail_extra"><a moz-do-not-send="true"
href="http://blogs.scalablelogic.com/2013/12/enhanced-networking-in-aws-cloud.html">http://blogs.scalablelogic.com/2013/12/enhanced-networking-in-aws-cloud.html</a><br>
          </div>
